Over the last two days , videos have emerged of regular police officers being thrashed by civilians in undisclosed locations , raising the question of just how physically and combat fit  kenya police officers are. Multiple sources at the police headquarters point of an unfit force , which has been precipitated by the sabotaging of compulsory refresher  training, that police officers were initially  undergoing  regularly, at the Kiganjo police training  school in Nyeri.   